a) Project Description

Project title
Recreational App (RecApp)


Project description
Healthy choice making for people's free time (for one day).

Target audience
All people need to make healthy free time choice.

Team members
Prathap Siva, prathap.sims@gmail.com
Sheng Chiu, sheng.chiu@shaw.ca


b) User Stories

A web app that helps groups of friends to vote on a preferred choice (using ranked voting), for example: "What movie should we see next Friday?".

Requirements:

* a user select the recreation with multiple choices
 -each recreation choice have 
  --a title
  --description

* when (a user visits the recreation he created thruough the submission_link) 
  -see a list of the choices for that recreation 
   --they enter their name if required

* date: google calender/schedule: one day, today

* the user
  -choose the choice(s) and 
  -then submits the chosed recreation

* each time a submission is received, 
  -the creator is notified with an email 
   which includes 
  --a link to the results (choices_link)

* the results are ranked using 
    the Borda Count method: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Borda_count




note: 
1. The only way to access the polls or see the results is via administrative links
2. This app does not follow the typical user authentication process: voters don't need to register or log in.